                        <interp inst="t18370814-name-326" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES STACK</persName>
                  </hi>. I am an officer of Covent Garden. I was on duty and saw the prisoner take this handkerchief from the prosecutor's left-hand cost pocket, and I took it from his breast.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner</hi>, If he saw me do it why did he ran after another boy? <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> He said he picked it up, but I saw him take it.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner receded a good character.)</p>
